SUMMARY:Jewish Book Club 2026
DESCRIPTION:Join the Center for Jewish Peoplehood for Jewish Book Club 2026! \nWe will be reading 6 books from Jewish Book Council’s new Nu Reads\, which is a curated\, reader-powered book subscription series that builds community\, strengthens the Jewish literary market\, and ensures Jewish voices are heard—and read. \n\nCheck out their page here: Nu Reads. You do not have to subscribe to Nu Reads to participate. \n\nContact Rachel Chancellor rchancellor@marinjcc.org for any questions.\n\nThis event is free of charge & open to all!
URL:https://www.marinjcc.org/event/jewish-book-club-2026/2026-04-07/
LOCATION:Osher Marin JCC – Isaac’s Gallery\, 200 North San Pedro Rd.\, San Rafael\, 94903\, United States
CATEGORIES:Jewish Life
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://www.marinjcc.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/web-updates-1-1.png
END:VEVENT
