SUMMARY:Game On! Mexican Train\, Rummikub & Scrabble
DESCRIPTION:Join others for a delightful afternoon of fun and games – literally! Choose from one of three games. Learn and play! \n\nMexican Train has become a popular game with dominos in which the goal is for participants to play all of the tiles from their hands onto one or more chains – or trains – emanating from a central hub or “station.” \n\nRummikub is a tile-based game for 2 or more players combining elements of the card game rummy and mahjong. \n\nScrabble is a popular word game for 2-4 players where participants use letter tiles to create words on a board\, aiming to connect them to existing words (similar to a crossword puzzle). \n\nPlayers of all levels are welcome! \n\nSpace is limited. Advance registration required.
