SUMMARY:Bay Area Excursion: Fabulous Filoli & Luscious Lovejoy's
DESCRIPTION:Board our private coach and leave the driving & parking to us on this wonderful daytrip to the Peninsula and San Francisco. \n\nVisit the Filoli Estate & Garden\, comprised of a 56-room manor house set on 16 acres of formal gardens\, surrounded by a 654-acre lot. Located in Woodside\, the estate is owned by the National Trust for Historic Preservation. \n\nHave free time to wonder through the house\, asking questions of docents in the various rooms. Then\, take a private guided tour of the gardens\, glorious in springtime. Stop by the gift shop of the way back to our coach. \nThen\, head to the city for a sumputous high tea at the adorable Lovejoy’s. \nReturn to Marin with tummy and soul filled! \n\nSpace is strictly limited and offered on a first-come\, first-served basis.
URL:https://www.marinjcc.org/event/bay-area-excursion-fabulous-filoli-luscious-lovejoys/
LOCATION:Filoli Historic House & Garden\, 86 Cañada Road\, Woodside\, CA\, 94062\, United States
CATEGORIES:Adult Learning
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/webp:https://www.marinjcc.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/image-1.webp
END:VEVENT
