SUMMARY:Midweek Musical Matinee: "Classical Guitar thru the Ages"
DESCRIPTION:Come join us for a live\, in-person concert filled with beautiful music and interesting insights. \n\nFan-favorite guitarist Marc Teicholz returns to play a concert of gorgeous works by master composers through the ages\, including Fernando Sor (1778-1839)\, Manuel Ponce (1882-1948)\, Joaquin Turina (1882-1949)\, and Sérgio Assad (1952-).
URL:https://www.marinjcc.org/event/midweek-musical-matinee-classical-guitar-thru-the-ages/
LOCATION:Osher Marin JCC\, 200 North San Pedro Road\, San Rafael\, CA\, 94903\, United States
CATEGORIES:Adult Learning
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/webp:https://www.marinjcc.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/image-3.webp
END:VEVENT
