SUMMARY:Midweek Musical Matinee: "Modern Masterpieces"
DESCRIPTION:Come join us for a live\, in-person concert filled with beautiful music and interesting insights. \n\nJoin pianist Keisuke Nakagoshi and violinist Patrick Galvin for a beautiful concert featuring music by three modern masters — Claude Debussy\, Sergei Prokofiev\, and Amy Beach — and a program that includes: \n\nC. Debussy – Sonata in g minor for Violin and Piano\, L. 140 \nS. Prokofiev – Sonata No. 1 in f minor for Violin and Piano\, Op. 80 \nA. Beach – Romance\, Op. 23
URL:https://www.marinjcc.org/event/midweek-musical-matinee-modern-masterpieces/
LOCATION:Osher Marin JCC\, 200 North San Pedro Road\, San Rafael\, CA\, 94903\, United States
CATEGORIES:Adult Learning
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/webp:https://www.marinjcc.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/image-4.webp
END:VEVENT
